        <div type="recipe">
        <p>Take very fine beaten Sugar, sifted thro’ a Lawn Sieve, make it up into a Paste, with Gum-Dragon very well steep’d in Rose-Water, or Orange-Flower-Water; beat it in a Mortar, squirt it, and bake it in a cool Oven. Colour the Red with Carmine, Blue with Powder-Blue, Yellow with steep’d Gamboodge put into Gum, and Yellow and Blue will make Green: Bake them after all other Puffs. Sugar the Papers well before you squirt the Puffs on Papers and Tin-Plates.</p>
            </div>
